<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="60">3.3. Displaying favourites</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>All menu paths saved as favourites are displayed in this tab. Favourites can also be deleted in this menu. Use the <strong>Up</strong> and <strong>Down</strong> arrows for sorting your favourites. This tab is only visible in your own user account. For further information about adding and deleting favourites , refer to the <strong><a href="/en/basics/working-with-plentymarkets/general-functions#80">Setting up general functions</a></strong> page of the manual.</p>
</div>
